{"tid":1911323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有露宿者目睹山哥被毁家當的經過，不敢評論: 「件事煲到咁大，我哋仲驚畀人搞」。","createTime":"2020-03-05T09:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T09:21:51.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7f003becc63b9229264a8398bed50ec3fcfc7a55","tid":1911323,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:03:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200305/s00001/1583393822792/%e7%a8%b1%e9%81%ad%e8%ad%a6%e8%b8%a2%e8%83%8c%e6%89%93%e7%88%9b%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%b6-%e9%9c%b2%e5%ae%bf%e8%80%85%e5%b1%b1%e5%93%a5%e8%b5%b4%e8%ad%a6%e7%bd%b2%e9%8c%84%e5%8f%a3%e4%be%9b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200305%2Fs00001%2F1583393822792%2F%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e9%2581%25ad%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25b8%25a2%25e8%2583%258c%25e6%2589%2593%25e7%2588%259b%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e7%2595%25b6-%25e9%259c%25b2%25e5%25ae%25bf%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%25b1%25b1%25e5%2593%25a5%25e8%25b5%25b4%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e9%258c%2584%25e5%258f%25a3%25e4%25be%259b&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=c0b68c0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200305%2Fs00001%2F1583393822792%2F%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e9%2581%25ad%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25b8%25a2%25e8%2583%258c%25e6%2589%2593%25e7%2588%259b%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e7%2595%25b6-%25e9%259c%25b2%25e5%25ae%25bf%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%25b1%25b1%25e5%2593%25a5%25e8%25b5%25b4%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%25bd%25b2%25e9%258c%2584%25e5%258f%25a3%25e4%25be%259b&h=97ad5e87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200305/s00001/1583393822792/%e7%a8%b1%e9%81%ad%e8%ad%a6%e8%b8%a2%e8%83%8c%e6%89%93%e7%88%9b%e5%ae%b6%e7%95%b6-%e9%9c%b2%e5%ae%bf%e8%80%85%e5%b1%b1%e5%93%a5%e8%b5%b4%e8%ad%a6%e7%bd%b2%e9%8c%84%e5%8f%a3%e4%be%9b</a><br />\n<br />\n深水埗警區上月24日在通州街公園一帶進行代號「晴天」的反罪惡行動，其間有警員被指破壞露宿者的家當。警方昨晚（4日）承認有警員涉毁壞現場物件，一名涉事警員被即時停職。今日（5日）下午，其中一名露宿者山哥被帶往警署錄口供。<br />\n<br />\n記者今午2時到公園，早前受訪稱警員腳踢其背、以球棍打爛其家當的露宿者山哥，正接受警員查詢。隨後西九龍重案組的警員陪同山哥上車，前往警署錄取口供。<br />\n<br />\n有露宿者目睹山哥被毁家當的經過，但不願透露細節和評論警方做法，稱「件事煲到咁大，我哋仲驚畀人搞」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200305/s00001/a0798d4a9be33d7fef4510cc1dfd2dc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200305%2Fs00001%2Fa0798d4a9be33d7fef4510cc1dfd2dc3.jpg&h=d8870832&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9925ea278d5e12d20b1c2c85b3dc1beb5201119","tid":1911323,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"畀白粉啲露宿者食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xe2eGKupc0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxe2eGKupc0k&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=e0efeb85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xe2eGKupc0k</a>"},{"pid":"4c0428e5e4388b4b1a6e2b9ac6ac867c46ba7bbf","tid":1911323,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"又揾自己友查自己友，睇下你查到啲乜"},{"pid":"0d2c081cf36b122a8d252d44db263eac0bf92cbd","tid":1911323,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"唔煲大唔通就唔會俾人搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc94063d97271067aa77418547e7f2cdc93fd335","tid":1911323,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqYULRo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqYULRo.png&h=a3e234c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"720ca0ee098783ae0a4d9f66d9fb54695b2a72b1","tid":1911323,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:10:38.000Z","msg":"中間隻狗女係